docs.lead_paragraph: Senate Democrats thwarted a Republican effort to ban late-term abortions on Tuesday as GOP leaders strained to avoid a government shutdown in eight days over the dispute — all against a tangled backdrop of presidential politics.

headline.main: Senate Blocks Anti-Abortion Bill; New Showdown Set
